{"Id":454286,"Title":"相逢行","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"卢青山","Context":"子为车，我为鞅；子为舟，我为桨；子为马，我为掌；子为水，我为浪。子欲歌，我为嗓；子欲泪，我为眶；子欲憩，憩我膀。梦生而为树，荫子之窗台；死则斫而为棺，抱子之残骸。死生荡簸，万劫轮回，司命徒酷，终不能劫子于予怀。此梦不谐，此心如丧，执子之手，泣子之裳上。明日别，各相忘。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"d2e87d21668fea869cf195cccd43ffbd","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":4870542,"Sentence":"子为马，我为掌；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi wéi mǎ ，wǒ wéi zhǎng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870543,"Sentence":"子为水，我为浪。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi wéi shui ，wǒ wéi làng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870544,"Sentence":"子欲歌，我为嗓；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi yù gē ，wǒ wéi sǎng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870545,"Sentence":"子欲泪，我为眶；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi yù lèi ，wǒ wéi kuàng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870546,"Sentence":"子欲憩，憩我膀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi yù qì ，qì wǒ bǎng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870540,"Sentence":"子为车，我为鞅；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi wéi chē ，wǒ wéi yāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870541,"Sentence":"子为舟，我为桨；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi wéi zhōu ，wǒ wéi jiǎng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870547,"Sentence":"梦生而为树，荫子之窗台；","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mèng shēng ér wéi shù ，yīn zi zhī chuāng tāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870548,"Sentence":"死则斫而为棺，抱子之残骸。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"si zé zhuó ér wéi guān ，bào zi zhī cán hái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":4870549,"Sentence":"死生荡簸，万劫轮回，司命徒酷，终不能劫子于予怀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyi